<div class="terms-of-use">
    <h2></h2>

    <div class="rich-text-field"><h2>welcome to essie Australia!</h2>
<p>ready to level up your manicures? discover a wide range of nail polish from essie Australia. with 8-free formula, our vegan nail polish collection is the key to a flawless and perfect manicure.&nbsp;<span style="font-size: 15px; white-space-collapse: preserve; background-color: #fff2cc; font-family: docs-Calibri; color: #000000;"><br />
</span></p>
<h2>essie nail polish collection</h2>
<p>with our vast range of nail polish collections, you can find your desired salon-like manicure looks with essie australia.<br />
<br />
go simple and classy with our <a href="https://www.essie.com.au/nail-polish/enamel/reds">enamel nail polish collection</a>. choose from our iconic and well-known nail polish shades, including&nbsp;<a href="https://www.essie.com.au/nail-polish/enamel/sheers/marshmallow-cloud-white-nail-polish">marshmallow cloud </a>and <a href="https://www.essie.com.au/nail-polish/enamel/sheers?selectedProduct=7">spaghetti strap.&nbsp;<br />
</a><br />
or, if you prefer a long-lasting gel finish, check out essie's <a href="https://www.essie.com.au/nail-polish/longwear/reds">long-wear nail polish</a> collection. featuring a 2-step fade-resistant formula, this essie nail polish collection will give you that gel-like shine with no base coat or harsh removal needed.&nbsp;<br />
<br />
tired of waiting for your nail polish to dry? discover essie's <a href="https://www.essie.com.au/nail-polish/quick-dry/blues">quick-dry nail polish</a> collection. with more than 20 on-trend colours to choose from, this vegan nail polish will get your nails ready in about a minute.&nbsp;</p>
<h2>base and top coats</h2>
<p>now that you've got your nail polish sorted, it's time to add that extra layer of foundation and protection with<a href="https://www.essie.com.au/base-and-top-coats/nail-base-coats"> base and top coats nail polish</a> range from essie.&nbsp;<br />
<br />
to start, apply one layer of your chosen<a href="https://www.essie.com.au/base-and-top-coats/nail-base-coats"> essie base coat nail polish</a> before colouring your nails. once done, select your desired finish from an array selection of <a href="https://www.essie.com.au/base-and-top-coats/nail-top-coats">top coats nail polish</a> to seal and protect your fresh nails.</p>
<h2>nail care &amp; treatment</h2>
<p>a perfect manicure and healthy nails go hand in hand, and <a href="https://www.essie.com.au/nail-care">essie nail care </a>collection can give you just that. discover our iconic <a href="https://www.essie.com.au/nail-care/cuticle-care/apricot-cuticle-oil">apricot cuticle oil</a> to help keep your cuticles hydrated and firm, or check out our <a href="https://www.essie.com.au/nail-care/treatment">nail strengthening and treatment collection</a> to complete your nail care routine. depending on your needs, essie's<a href="https://www.essie.com.au/nail-care/treatment/hard-to-resist-nail-strengthener-pink-tint"> hard to resist nail polish range </a>supports nail recovery and gives your nails that natural glow.&nbsp;<br />
<br />
<br />
looking for more? head to our<a href="https://www.essie.com.au/nail-art-guides"> nail art section</a> for a step by step guide on creating your dream nail designs, or check out the <a href="https://www.essie.com.au/nail-tips-and-inspirations">tips &amp; inspirations</a> section for all-things nails from essie Australia.&nbsp;</p></div>
</div>

    function getHParamImgUrl(url) {
        let result = "";
        const indexOfH = url.indexOf("h=");

        for (let i = indexOfH; i < url.length; i += 1) {
            result += url.charAt(i);
            if (url.charAt(i + 1) === "&") {
                break;
            }
        }
        
        return result;
    }

    function getSrc(param) {
        let resultUrl = param.url;
        const hParam = getHParamImgUrl(param.url);

        return resultUrl.split(hParam).join("");
    }

                            social_network: name,

                        };
                        window.dataLayer.push(taggingEvent);
                    });
                });

    <script type="text/javascript">
        function getUrlParameter(name) {
            name = name.replace(/[\[]/, '\\[').replace(/[\]]/, '\\]');
            var regex = new RegExp('[\\?&]' + name + '=([^&#]*)');
            var results = regex.exec(location.search);
            return results === null ? '' : decodeURIComponent(results[1].replace(/\+/g, ' '));
        };

        var socialLoginEvent = '{&quot;event&quot;:&quot;uaevent&quot;,&quot;ecommerce&quot;:&quot;undefined&quot;,&quot;eventCategory&quot;:&quot;log in&quot;,&quot;eventAction&quot;:&quot;social::facebook&quot;,&quot;eventLabel&quot;:&quot;successful&quot;}';
